# dlog

 A CLI tool to track your dev sessions.

 ## Usage
 ```bash
 dlg start "ProjectName"
 dlg note "what you did"
 dlg stop
 dlg stats
 dlg export
 ```

 ## Installation
 ```bash
 git clone https://github.com/abdoulayecodes/dlog
 cd Dlog
 pip install -r requirements.txt
```
